Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:09.88,2,,0,0,0,,Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.31,0:00:11.68,2,,0,0,0,,Air.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:13.52,2,,0,0,0,,Water.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.21,0:00:18.83,2,,0,0,0,,Only the Avatar can master all four elements
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.21,0:00:21.01,2,,0,0,0,,and bring balance to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,土强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,火烈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.31,0:00:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,气和
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,水善
