Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.81,0:00:26.98,3,,0,0,0,,{\fs200\t(0,200,0.5,\fs30)\pos(363,391)}{\fad(0,200)}降世神通：科拉传奇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:30.19,2,,0,0,0,,After fusing with Vaatu, Unalaq became a dark Avatar
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.20,0:00:31.96,2,,0,0,0,,and ripped Korra and Raava apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.46,0:00:33.53,2,,0,0,0,,By destroying Raava,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.56,0:00:37.67,2,,0,0,0,,Unalaq and Vaatu transformed into the most powerful dark spirit that's ever lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.16,0:00:41.12,2,,0,0,0,,Tenzin managed to free Jinora from the fog of lost souls,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.15,0:00:43.67,2,,0,0,0,,but her spiritual quest isn't over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:46.63,2,,0,0,0,,Can anyone save the world from eternal darkness?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,融合了瓦图之后，吴纳克变成了暗黑逆神通
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.20,0:00:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,并且分离了科拉和拉瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.46,0:00:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,摧毁拉瓦后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.56,0:00:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,吴纳克和瓦图变成了有史以来最强大的黑暗神灵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.16,0:00:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,丹增设法从迷魂雾中将吉诺拉解救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.15,0:00:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但是她的灵界之旅还没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,有谁能从永恒的黑暗中拯救这个世界吗？
