Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.91,0:00:50.98,3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(361,253)\c&H000000&\2c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\fad(1600,600)}第二册：神灵篇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.75,0:01:01.71,2,,0,0,0,,Pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:04.22,2,,0,0,0,,General Iroh, are your ships in position?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.37,0:01:07.47,2,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mr. president, but I need to know what kind of enemy we're dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.53,0:01:22.67,2,,0,0,0,,It's time to take back the physical world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:29.48,2,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:56.98,2,,0,0,0,,Monster attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:11.41,2,,0,0,0,,They're over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:14.26,2,,0,0,0,,Please, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.22,0:02:17.41,2,,0,0,0,,They're going to be all right,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:20.25,2,,0,0,0,,but I need to get them into some spirit water right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.67,0:02:50.04,2,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness you're all okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.82,0:02:51.82,2,,0,0,0,,Did you find Jinora?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.99,0:02:53.76,2,,0,0,0,,I was able to rescue her soul,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:56.36,2,,0,0,0,,but she wasn't ready to return to her body yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:02:58.74,2,,0,0,0,,She sense the world was in grave danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:00.59,2,,0,0,0,,She was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:04.85,2,,0,0,0,,Were you able to stop Unalaq and Vaatu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:07.11,2,,0,0,0,,No, they fused,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:10.34,2,,0,0,0,,then Vaatu ripped Raava right out of me and destroyed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:12.16,2,,0,0,0,,Vaatu won.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:15.15,2,,0,0,0,,No! I'm too young
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:17.34,2,,0,0,0,,to live through 10,000 years of darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.52,0:03:19.99,2,,0,0,0,,Korra, can't you talk to one of your past lives or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:22.45,2,,0,0,0,,When Vaatu destroyed Raava,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:26.15,2,,0,0,0,,he destroyed my connection to the past Avatars too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.77,0:03:28.10,2,,0,0,0,,If that's true, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:29.66,2,,0,0,0,,the cycle is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:32.80,2,,0,0,0,,I'm the last Avatar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:35.05,2,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Tenzin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.27,0:03:45.79,2,,0,0,0,,She needs you now, more than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.22,0:03:57.38,2,,0,0,0,,It's going to destroy the entire city.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:15.39,2,,0,0,0,,We're going down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:52.44,2,,0,0,0,,It's pandemonium in the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:54.99,2,,0,0,0,,Giant vines are destroying everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:57.67,2,,0,0,0,,This is Shiro Shinobi signing off...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:10.37,2,,0,0,0,,Zhu Li, commence operation "winged freedom!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.32,0:05:17.53,2,,0,0,0,,Do the thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.62,0:05:27.60,2,,0,0,0,,The other Avatars may not be able to help you anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:29.67,2,,0,0,0,,but perhaps I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:31.43,2,,0,0,0,,No one can help me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:35.37,2,,0,0,0,,I know I haven't been the best mentor to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:40.20,2,,0,0,0,,but I realized it was because I had a lot of spiritual growth to do myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:42.91,2,,0,0,0,,There may still be a way for you to stop Vaatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:44.15,2,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:47.62,2,,0,0,0,,Let go of your attachment to who you <i>think</i> you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.06,0:05:49.95,2,,0,0,0,,and connect with your inner spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.11,0:05:52.09,2,,0,0,0,,Haven't you heard anything I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:54.00,2,,0,0,0,,Raava is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.73,0:05:56.62,2,,0,0,0,,I'm not connected to a spirit anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:58.40,2,,0,0,0,,I'm not talking about Raava.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.91,0:06:00.88,2,,0,0,0,,Raava is not who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:02.51,2,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.12,0:06:04.37,2,,0,0,0,,I need to show you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.08,0:06:10.12,2,,0,0,0,,Why are you showing me Vaatu's prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:13.99,2,,0,0,0,,Because this tree had a history long before it held Vaatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.80,0:06:17.06,2,,0,0,0,,This is the tree of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:22.65,2,,0,0,0,,And the legends say that its roots bind the spirit and physical worlds together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.22,0:06:26.92,2,,0,0,0,,And you think this tree can help me somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:27.71,2,,0,0,0,,Yes, I have read that long ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:32.23,2,,0,0,0,,the ancients would meditate beneath this tree
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:35.76,2,,0,0,0,,and connect with the great cosmic energy of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:46.03,2,,0,0,0,,These are my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.95,0:06:48.83,2,,0,0,0,,The tree of time remembers all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:53.45,2,,0,0,0,,Korra, the most powerful thing about you is not the spirit of Raava,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:55.47,2,,0,0,0,,but your own inner spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:59.50,2,,0,0,0,,You have always been strong, unyielding, and fearless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:01.51,2,,0,0,0,,Avatar Wan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:03.71,2,,0,0,0,,Before he fused with Raava,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:05.66,2,,0,0,0,,Wan was just a regular person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:09.80,2,,0,0,0,,But he was brave and smart
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.23,0:07:12.06,2,,0,0,0,,and always wanted to defend the helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:12.73,2,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.34,0:07:15.67,2,,0,0,0,,He became a legend because of who he was,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:16.85,2,,0,0,0,,not what he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:21.44,2,,0,0,0,,He wasn't defined by Raava any more than you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:29.72,2,,0,0,0,,Everyone in Republic City is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.12,0:07:31.23,2,,0,0,0,,You have to help them, Korra.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.44,0:07:32.01,2,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.35,0:07:33.67,2,,0,0,0,,They're halfway around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:35.71,2,,0,0,0,,Do as the ancients once did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:38.91,2,,0,0,0,,Connect to the cosmic energy of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:43.41,2,,0,0,0,,Don't bend the elements, but the energy within yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:45.88,2,,0,0,0,,You really think I can do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:48.58,2,,0,0,0,,I have no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:53.77,2,,0,0,0,,Thank you for not giving up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.35,0:07:55.22,2,,0,0,0,,I'm proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.31,0:08:10.09,2,,0,0,0,,If you and Vaatu have the same fight every 10,000 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:12.07,2,,0,0,0,,why hasn't one of you destroyed the other?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:16.28,2,,0,0,0,,He cannot destroy light any more than I can destroy darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:19.08,2,,0,0,0,,One cannot exist without the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:22.34,2,,0,0,0,,Find the light in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:22.43,2,,0,0,0,,Uh... What did you say to her, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:57.38,2,,0,0,0,,Korra's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:10:00.18,2,,0,0,0,,And she's a blue giant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.67,0:11:07.99,2,,0,0,0,,You are looking for something that is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:11.81,2,,0,0,0,,Raava has been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:15.14,2,,0,0,0,,And soon you will be too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:32.04,2,,0,0,0,,They're coming for Korra.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.45,0:12:37.00,2,,0,0,0,,Leave my Bolin alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.46,0:12:39.84,2,,0,0,0,,I am so done with spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.18,0:12:42.18,2,,0,0,0,,Eska! I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.77,0:12:47.32,2,,0,0,0,,Let's face the end of the world together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:49.14,2,,0,0,0,,You're so romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:57.50,2,,0,0,0,,With you out of the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:01.89,2,,0,0,0,,I will be the one true Avatar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:12.25,2,,0,0,0,,Mommy, it's Jinora.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:14.73,2,,0,0,0,,She's... Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.95,0:13:16.35,2,,0,0,0,,What? Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:20.70,2,,0,0,0,,Be careful, sweetie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:43.38,2,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:47.19,2,,0,0,0,,Raava.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.18,0:14:48.29,2,,0,0,0,,Go in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:52.03,2,,0,0,0,,Harmonic convergence is nearly over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:55.99,2,,0,0,0,,We must return to the spirit world so we can fuse once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:01.65,2,,0,0,0,,I'll see you soon, dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.11,0:16:25.12,2,,0,0,0,,Gran-gran, I missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:28.85,2,,0,0,0,,What about Korra and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:31.60,2,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. They're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.18,0:16:33.47,2,,0,0,0,,Korra saved the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:32.18,2,,0,0,0,,Her Avatar spirit has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.92,0:17:45.77,2,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:01.05,2,,0,0,0,,I don't even know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.07,0:18:02.89,2,,0,0,0,,You were amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.07,0:18:05.90,2,,0,0,0,,And the way you turned all gigantic like that, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:07.81,2,,0,0,0,,I just wish Varrick had been here to film it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.01,0:18:09.80,2,,0,0,0,,It would have been the greatest mover ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.93,0:18:12.66,2,,0,0,0,,After <i>the Nuktuk chronicles,</i> of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:17.03,2,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about your father,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.31,0:18:19.44,2,,0,0,0,,but he was already fused with Vaatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.21,0:18:21.14,2,,0,0,0,,I couldn't save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:24.11,2,,0,0,0,,It seems cousin Korra is under the impression
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:26.33,2,,0,0,0,,we are saddened by our father's demise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:28.13,2,,0,0,0,,But I will not miss him at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:30.93,2,,0,0,0,,In the end, he became a deplorable man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.53,0:18:32.37,2,,0,0,0,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:35.09,2,,0,0,0,,But how will we explain this to mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:39.85,2,,0,0,0,,So I was thinking, I'm not really a fan of the long-distance relationship thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:42.65,2,,0,0,0,,So how about you move to Republic City with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.57,0:18:45.54,2,,0,0,0,,I do not think that will be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.38,0:18:48.78,2,,0,0,0,,Okay, Desna can come too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.33,0:18:50.79,2,,0,0,0,,I will not be joining you, Bolin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:53.29,2,,0,0,0,,Desna and I must return home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.72,0:18:54.66,2,,0,0,0,,But you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:56.75,2,,0,0,0,,Eternal darkness was upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:18:58.69,2,,0,0,0,,I became caught up in the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:01.02,2,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.22,0:19:03.53,2,,0,0,0,,I guess I did too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:08.70,2,,0,0,0,,But... You will always hold a special place in the organ that pumps my blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:12.78,2,,0,0,0,,I will remember you fondly, my turtle-duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:19.49,2,,0,0,0,,Bum-Ju, you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.33,0:19:22.30,2,,0,0,0,,I missed you, little buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:30.38,2,,0,0,0,,Now that you're bonded with Raava once again,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:33.57,2,,0,0,0,,are you also reconnected to your past lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.01,0:19:35.40,2,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.51,0:19:38.29,2,,0,0,0,,I think that link is gone forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:40.08,2,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:44.16,2,,0,0,0,,Why don't you close the portals and we'll go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.53,0:19:53.63,2,,0,0,0,,Maybe I shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.81,0:19:55.48,2,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.79,0:20:01.86,2,,0,0,0,,What if Unalaq was right when he said the Avatar shouldn't be a bridge between the two worlds?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:06.16,2,,0,0,0,,What if Avatar Wan made a mistake when he closed the portals?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.38,0:20:10.27,2,,0,0,0,,What if humans and spirits weren't meant to live apart?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:14.74,2,,0,0,0,,Well, what do you think I should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:18.03,2,,0,0,0,,I think you should trust your instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:20.62,2,,0,0,0,,There is nothing else I can teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:22.92,2,,0,0,0,,You are the Avatar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.94,0:20:26.44,2,,0,0,0,,Whatever your decision, I support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:43.20,2,,0,0,0,,Hey, can we talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:44.27,2,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:47.14,2,,0,0,0,,There's something I've been wanting to tell you about that fight we had.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:49.48,2,,0,0,0,,I know I said it wasn't that bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.88,0:20:51.14,2,,0,0,0,,but that's not exactly true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.44,0:20:55.28,2,,0,0,0,,I, um... I broke up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.76,0:20:57.62,2,,0,0,0,,I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:21:00.48,2,,0,0,0,,But I thought you said you lost part of your memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:03.87,2,,0,0,0,,I did, but being inside the tree of time brought it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:07.11,2,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for blowing up at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:08.04,2,,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:10.84,2,,0,0,0,,I think we both said some things that we regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.26,0:21:13.39,2,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you just tell me the truth in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.63,0:21:14.87,2,,0,0,0,,I know I should have, but
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.89,0:21:17.75,2,,0,0,0,,I didn't wanna hurt you all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:20.50,2,,0,0,0,,I guess part of me wanted to forget about the breakup too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.17,0:21:22.94,2,,0,0,0,,I think we both know that this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:24.84,2,,0,0,0,,Us...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.32,0:21:27.12,2,,0,0,0,,Doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.77,0:21:28.35,2,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:31.06,2,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:32.89,2,,0,0,0,,For real this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:46.84,2,,0,0,0,,I'll always love you, Korra.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.26,0:21:48.55,2,,0,0,0,,And I'll always love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.23,0:21:57.95,2,,0,0,0,,You want a hug?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.33,0:22:07.68,2,,0,0,0,,The war of the water tribes is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.53,0:22:10.19,2,,0,0,0,,Unalaq has been defeated
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:12.53,2,,0,0,0,,and the northern fleet is returning home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.18,0:22:15.65,2,,0,0,0,,The water tribes will always be allies,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.20,0:22:19.17,2,,0,0,0,,but the Southern tribe is now independent.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:21.24,2,,0,0,0,,And the Southern council of elders
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.38,0:22:23.91,2,,0,0,0,,has appointed my father, Tonraq,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.03,0:22:25.65,2,,0,0,0,,to be your new chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.59,0:22:33.75,2,,0,0,0,,I've realized that even though we should learn from those who came before us,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.51,0:22:36.36,2,,0,0,0,,we must also forge our own path.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.96,0:22:42.00,2,,0,0,0,,So that is why I've decided to keep the portals open.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.54,0:22:45.08,2,,0,0,0,,Humans can now physically enter the spirit world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.11,0:22:48.07,2,,0,0,0,,and spirits will be free to roam our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.96,0:22:50.56,2,,0,0,0,,I will no longer be the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.39,0:22:54.63,2,,0,0,0,,Humans and spirits must learn to live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:22:59.07,2,,0,0,0,,My mission will always be to use Raava's light spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:02.00,2,,0,0,0,,to guide the world toward peace and balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.45,0:23:05.88,2,,0,0,0,,Harmonic convergence has caused a shift in the planet's energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.33,0:23:07.29,2,,0,0,0,,I can feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.38,0:23:10.35,2,,0,0,0,,Things will never be the same again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.05,0:23:13.37,2,,0,0,0,,We are entering a new age.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.75,0:01:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,艾洛将军，你的舰队就位了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.37,0:01:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，总统先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我得知道，我们要对付的是什么样的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.53,0:01:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是时候夺回物质世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,开火！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,怪物发动攻击了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托，快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.22,0:02:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我得马上把他们放到灵水里面去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.67,0:02:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,谢天谢地，你们都没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.82,0:02:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你找到吉诺拉了没有？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.99,0:02:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我本可以救出她的魂魄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但是她还没打算回到她的身体里面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:02:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,她感觉世界正在极度危险之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,她是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你阻止吴纳克和瓦图了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不，他们融合了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,然后瓦图把拉瓦从我身体里拉了出来并且摧毁了她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦图赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不！我的寿命短暂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,可没法在黑暗的岁月中活一万年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.52,0:03:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,科拉，你现在不能去和前世对话之类的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,当瓦图摧毁了拉瓦时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他也切断了我和前世神通们的联系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.77,0:03:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,如果那是真的，那么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,轮回终结了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是最后的降世神通了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的很抱歉，丹增
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.27,0:03:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,她现在比任何时候都更需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.22,0:03:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他要摧毁整座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在坠落
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,街上真是一团乱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,巨藤正在摧毁一切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是忍四郎，现场为您报道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,朱莉，开始执行“自由之翼”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.32,0:05:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,打开机器！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.62,0:05:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,其他的神通恐怕是帮不上你什么忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但是或许我能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,现在谁也帮不了我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道，我可能算不上是你最好的导师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我认识到这是因为我自己在精神上也有很多需要成长的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你也许还有个办法可以阻止瓦图
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,什么办法？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,放开你对自我身份的执着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.06,0:05:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,并且和你本来的自我灵魂相连
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.11,0:05:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你没把我说的话听进去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,拉瓦已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.73,0:05:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我再也无法和神灵相连接了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是在说拉瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.91,0:06:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,拉瓦并不是真正的你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.12,0:06:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我要让你看一些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.08,0:06:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你要给我看瓦图的监牢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这棵树的历史在囚禁瓦图之前就早有了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.80,0:06:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这是时间之树
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,传说它的根把灵界和人界连接在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.22,0:06:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得这棵树还能帮得上我？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,对，我很久以前就从书上了解到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,古人们在这棵树中冥思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,与宇宙的无限能量相连接
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这都是我的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.95,0:06:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,时间之树能记得一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,科拉，你最强大之处并不是拉瓦神灵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,而是你自己内心深处的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你始终都强大，无畏，不屈不挠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,神通万
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,在他和拉瓦融合之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是个平常人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他又勇敢又聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.23,0:07:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,总是乐于保护弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.34,0:07:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他之所以成为传奇是因为他是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是他是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他的自我并没有比你更多地由拉瓦来定义
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,共和城内的所有人都在危险之中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.12,0:07:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须拯救他们，科拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.44,0:07:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.35,0:07:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他们离我们有半个世界远
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就像古人曾经做过的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,和宇宙的能量相连接
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不是控制元素，而是去控制你内在的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的认为我能做到？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我毫不怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你没有放弃我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.35,0:07:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我真为你骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.31,0:08:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你和瓦图每一万年就要战斗一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你们中没有任何一个被摧毁？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗是无法战胜光明的，同理光明也无法消灭黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们两个是互相依存的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,找到暗中之光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟她到底说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,科拉回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:10:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,而且她成了个蓝色巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.67,0:11:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你要寻找的东西已经不复存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,拉瓦已经被我杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就轮到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他们来抓科拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.45,0:12:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,离我的波林远点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.46,0:12:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经受够神灵了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.18,0:12:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,爱丝卡，我爱你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.77,0:12:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们一起来面对世界末日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你还真是浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,只要消灭了你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我就能成为唯一真正的神通
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈，是吉诺拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,她……好美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.95,0:13:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,小心点，甜心！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:28.91,5,,0,0,0,,吉诺拉手上的是光明灵蝶，别忘了上集结尾哦……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:46.38,5,,0,0,0,,拉瓦与光明灵蝶产生共鸣，在瓦图体内的具体位置暴露出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,拉瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.18,0:14:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,平静下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,谐波汇聚快要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须回到灵界，好再次融合
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,一会儿见，爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.11,0:16:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,奶奶，我好想你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,科拉和其他人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.18,0:16:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,科拉拯救了世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,她的神通之魂也回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.92,0:17:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不知道该怎么说才好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.07,0:18:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你简直太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.07,0:18:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你变成巨人的那种场景
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我真希望瓦里克能在现场把它录下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.01,0:18:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那将是有史以来最棒的电影
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.93,0:18:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,当然，在《纳塔克历险记》之后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你们父亲的事我很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.31,0:18:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但他已经和瓦图合体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.21,0:18:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法挽救他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来科拉是怕我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,受到父亲之死的打击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不过事实上我一点都不想念他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,到最后，他已经让我们愤恨不已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.53,0:18:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我同意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们该怎么向母亲解释呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我想，我可接受不了异地恋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,所以，你搬到共和城来如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.57,0:18:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.38,0:18:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，杰斯纳也可以来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.33,0:18:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能跟着你了，波林
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,杰斯纳和我必须回家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.72,0:18:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但你说过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,当时在我们面前的是永恒的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:18:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那一刻我有点迷糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.22,0:19:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不过，你在我的心中，会一直占据特殊的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我会深情地想念着你，我的小龟鸭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,小布，你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.33,0:19:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,小伙计，我好想你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你又一次跟拉瓦合体了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那么你还能联系到你的前世们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.01,0:19:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.51,0:19:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为和他们的联系已经永远断掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不关掉通道，然后我们回家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.53,0:19:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我不该这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.81,0:19:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.79,0:20:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,如果吴纳克没错，如他所说神通不该是两个世界的桥梁？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,如果神通万关闭通道的确是一个错误？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.38,0:20:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,如果人类和神灵本不应该分居两界？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，你认为我应该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为你应该相信你的直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这里已经没有什么是我可以教给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你是降世神通
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.94,0:20:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,无论你做出什么决定，我都会支持你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨，我们能聊聊吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,有点事情我一直想告诉你，关于我们的吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我说过那没有那么严重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.88,0:20:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但是那不是真相
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.44,0:20:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我，呃…我和你分手了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.76,0:20:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:21:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,可是，我以为你说你丧失了部分记忆？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,的确是这样，但在时间之树里，我找回了记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉我对你发了火
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们都说了让我们后悔的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.26,0:21:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么当初你不告诉我真相？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.63,0:21:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我本该这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.89,0:21:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我不想再次伤害你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我的部分内心也想让我忘记这次分手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.17,0:21:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为我们都知道这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.32,0:21:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.77,0:21:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这次真的结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都很爱你，科拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.26,0:21:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我也一直爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.23,0:21:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要一个拥抱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.33,0:22:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,水族内战结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.53,0:22:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,吴纳克被击败
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,而且北方水族舰队正在返回家乡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.18,0:22:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,南北水族部落将永远是盟友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.20,0:22:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在南极水族部落已经独立
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,而南水族的长老议会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.38,0:22:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,任命我的父亲，托纳克
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.03,0:22:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,成为你们新的族长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.59,0:22:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道，虽然我们应该从前人身上学习
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.51,0:22:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们也必须修筑我们自己前进的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.96,0:22:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我为什么决定要保持通道开放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.54,0:22:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,人类现在可以亲身进入灵界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.11,0:22:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,而神灵也会自在地在我们的世界畅游
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.96,0:22:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我将不再是两界的桥梁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.39,0:22:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,人类和神灵必须学会一同生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:22:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我的使命将永远是运用拉瓦的光明的灵力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,去引导世界走向和平与平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.45,0:23:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,谐波汇聚使得这个星球的能量发生了变化
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.33,0:23:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我能感受到它
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.38,0:23:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,事物将与曾经再不相同
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.05,0:23:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在进入一个新的时代
